{"tid":1298093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人領養依隻藍衫芝娃娃？？？","createTime":"2019-07-08T18:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T17:15:54.000Z","uid":11374,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"182489f5761481ed457cfd218fa8f8c3a7629278","tid":1298093,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:36:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QkoOJjA3wvo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQkoOJjA3wvo&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dpuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=bb00754e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QkoOJjA3wvo</a><br />\n<br />\n0:45開始睇<br />\n個廢柴咩住2支旗係後面 屌你老母 負責舉旗嫁咋<br />\n柒唔柒呀你 中學運動會都冇人肯做啦 慘撚過幼稚園扮樹<br />\n仲係到聲大大<br />\n比白衫養狗咁養 叫佢退後 即刻聲都唔敢聲<br />\n<br />\n好撚慘呀 谷撚到成肚氣 想扑鳩市民都冇得扑<br />\n要負責企係後面舉旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039f374ce9cee52c810d9d6967ed6ae14cbd106c","tid":1298093,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:38:37.000Z","msg":"今次毅俊星 都不屌?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34f567c8a045619b72ace142d128b9d4d46c299","tid":1298093,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"189e1b46df6aea7240b90c19e55bce5711ff0de0","tid":1298093,"uid":11374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:42:39.000Z","msg":"倒及芝娃娃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65507980df54b5ebe02ae685f1ddf4f0e5106c4","tid":1298093,"uid":149566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor